title: Cindy Li
text:

A little about me… - I’ve lived in 3 countries - A Swiftie! Taylor Swift followed me on tumblr. - I love to sew so I am passionate about sustainable fashion and how technology can reduce the environmental/social impacts of the fashion industry.
